### .screenrc

## remap Ctrl-a to backtick
escape ``

## enable 256 color term
term screen-256color

## screen buffer
defscrollback 4096

## no flash
vbell off

## no start message
startup_message off

## stop screen from catching C-S and C-Q, XON and XOFF
defflow off

## scroll
termcapinfo st* ti@:te@

## Evil evil keybindings. Do Not Want!
bind ^h
bind h
bind ^Q
bind q
bind ^S
bind s
bind ^X
bind x
bind ^Z
bind z

## Window numbering starts at 1, not 0.
bind c screen 1
bind ^c screen 1
bind 0 select 10                                                            
screen 1

## Fix for residual editor text
altscreen on

## hardstatus
hardstatus alwayslastline
hardstatus string "%{.g}%w %= %H"

## windowlist
windowlist string "%4n %h%=%f"
